ğŸ“˜ 1. Project Overview
Project Name

Student Management System â€“ Salesforce LWC

Project Description

The Student Management System is a Salesforce Lightning Web Component (LWC)â€“based application designed to manage student records efficiently. The application supports full CRUD operations (Create, Read, Update, Delete) and provides advanced UI features such as search, sorting, pagination, dashboard summaries, and visual analytics using charts.

The project demonstrates real-world Salesforce development practices using Apex, Lightning Web Components, parent-child communication, and Salesforce UI best practices.

ğŸ¯ Project Objectives

To create a user-friendly interface for managing student data
To implement real-time UI updates without page refresh
To demonstrate integration of Apex with LWC
To provide dashboard-level insights using summary cards and charts
To follow modular and reusable component design

